                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6970" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1083</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8619 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破茧离巢能终向荣吗？—复星医药分拆复宏汉霖上市</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Whether the cocoon out of the nest can be glorious—Fosun Pharma spin-off FuHong Henlius listed</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张军波，谭广斌，黎绮华，耿天姿，吴毓泰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海复宏汉霖生物技术有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">复宏汉霖；资本运作；分拆上市；市场效应；企业价值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FuHong Henlius； Capital Operation； Spin-off Listing； Market Effect；Enterprise Value</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">春江水暖鸭先知。随着国内分拆上市制度逐渐成熟，更多企业投身于分拆上市，资本市场上投资者尤为关注分拆上市企业的市场价值与业绩。本案例重点描述复宏汉霖分拆上市后续经营状况变化，复宏汉霖为实现可持续发展，进行股权结构改革。而在分拆上市后，公司过得还好吗？通过观察复宏汉霖市场价值的变动，以及对比研发投入和营收增长等来分析企业的业绩情况，发现在分拆上市后不仅实现产品商业化，还取得很大成效。本案例聚焦于分析对比分拆上市前后其经营状况，简单描述复宏汉霖分拆上市的动因、过程，旨在引导学员理解分拆上市对企业产生的融资效应和市场价值效应，进而提高对中国企业分拆上市资本运作行为的分析和价值判断能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Spring River water warm duck prophet. With the maturity of the domestic split listing system, more and more companies are involved in the split listing, and investors pay more attention to the market value and performance of the split listed companies. This case mainly describes the following changes in the management of the split listing of Fuhong Henlius, Fuhong Henlius to achieve sustainable development, share ownership structure reform.. And after the spin-off, how&#39;s the company doing? By observing the change of market value of Fuhong Henlius, and comparing the R&amp;D Investment and revenue growth, we found that after the split listing, not only the commercialization of products, but also achieved great results. This case focuses on the analysis and comparison of its operation before and after the split listing, and briefly describes the motivation and process of the split listing of Fuhong henlius, the purpose of this study is to guide students to understand the financing effect and market value effect of spin-off, and then improve the operation of China&#39;s enterprises split listed capital analysis and value judgment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《公司理财》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分拆上市的概念及条件；分拆上市的动因理论；上市后的企业融资效应；企业的市场价值效应；企业上市后的绩效研究</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
